paragraph: Sitting in front of her computer screen, Suzune Hiragi stared at a gaming profile that bore an uncanny resemblance to herself. She thought about reaching out to Rain-chan, perhaps to inquire if someone had mistakenly used her identity. Maybe an automatic feature of the app could have captured her profile image from her phone's contact list without her knowledge. Regardless, she felt compelled to verify the situation before it got any more complicated.
